      "id": "PopularPost43191",
      "post_content": "I don't think you can set up an infinite loop with two of these, since it says \"whenever a *card* is played\" not a spell. The errata says \"whenever a player casts a card\" (which sounds silly, but w/e) which works to the same effect.  \n  \nBut [Raven's Crime](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raven's Crime) with [Mind Funeral](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Funeral)! Agh! Dirty! I'm looking forward to making many different decks around this card. Looks like a fun and reasonably challenging combo card to set up. 4/5",
      "posted_by": "Ritius",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost43191\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">I don't think you can set up an infinite loop with two of these, since it says \"whenever a <i>card</i> is played\" not a spell. The errata says \"whenever a player casts a card\" (which sounds silly, but w/e) which works to the same effect.<br/><br/>But <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raven's Crime\">Raven's Crime</a> with <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Funeral\">Mind Funeral</a>! Agh! Dirty! I'm looking forward to making many different decks around this card. Looks like a fun and reasonably challenging combo card to set up. 4/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy17122\">Ritius</span>\r\n                                (12/29/2009 6:36:09 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars